main_body:
The Internal Agreement is amended as follows:
1. In the table in Article 1(2)(a) the round brackets and asterisk after the words ‘Bulgaria’ and ‘Romania’ and the footnote ‘(*) Estimated amount’ shall be deleted;
2. In the table in Article 8(2) the following shall be deleted:
(a) the round brackets and asterisk after the words ‘Bulgaria’ and ‘Romania’ and the square brackets in the second column of those same rows;
(b) the footnote ‘(*) Estimated vote’;
(c) the row ‘Total EU-25’, ‘999’;
(d) the round brackets and asterisk as well as the square brackets in the row ‘Total EU-27 (*)’‘[1 004]’.
3. Article 8(3) shall be replaced by the following:
